description: Two small hunters stand by a stream in a clearing filled with tree stumps, looking at the massive, felled body of a blue creature with long tusks. Above the creature looms a colossal axe embedded in the ground next to an equally giant, spiked boot, suggesting an unseen enormous entity was responsible. The scene creates dark, absurd humor through the extreme discrepancy in scale between the hunters and their apparent quarry/competitor. It presents a surreal hunting scenario far removed from typical game.
caption: Uh-oh, Stan. I guess it wasn't a big, blue mule deer.
